ives compasses and such not so easy to notice in the off chance i decide to be visible i prefer not to be since walking quietly away from active areas increases the number of non human type critters i see james james s cochrane when in danger or in doubt run in this space gt six five one one a prism gatech edu circles scream and shout for rent